# Project Structure Overview

This is a Next.js project with a blog functionality and potentially other features.

## Key Directories

- [src/app](mdc:src/app) - Contains the Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- [src/components](mdc:src/components) - Contains reusable UI components organized by feature
- [src/lib](mdc:src/lib) - Contains utility functions and libraries
- [src/types](mdc:src/types) - Contains TypeScript type definitions
- [src/hooks](mdc:src/hooks) - Contains React hooks
- [content](mdc:content) - Contains MDX blog posts managed by ContentLayer
- [public](mdc:public) - Contains static assets

## Main Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [contentlayer.config.ts](mdc:contentlayer.config.ts) - ContentLayer configuration for blog content
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration
